name: challenge12
description: * Feature Tasks      * Create a new class called pseudo queue.     * Do not use an existing Queue.     * Instead, this PseudoQueue class will implement our standard queue interface (the two methods listed below),     * Internally, utilize 2 Stack instances to create and manage the queue     *   Methods:     * enqueue     * Arguments: value     * Inserts value into the PseudoQueue, using a first-in, first-out approach.     * dequeue     * Arguments: none     * Extracts a value from the PseudoQueue, using a first-in, first-out approach.
